論文名稱(中文) 
      
國立成功大學臨時人員員工權益知覺與組織承諾之研究


論文名稱(英文) 
      
Relationship between Contracting Staffs’ Perceived Employee Rights and Interests and Organizational Commitment at National Cheng Kung University


